    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Well-kept good-condition car that runs and drives nicely. It presents well overall with a clean appearance inside and out, though it does show normal age- and use-related wear in places rather than a like-new finish. The interior is solid and comfortable, and the exterior still has a respectable look with typical minor imperfections you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle. A buyer can expect an honest, dependable car that has been cared for, but not a flawless showpiece.",
