    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option with straightforward appeal for someone seeking low-cost mobility, a project, or a practical spare vehicle. Priced to reflect its condition while still presenting an opportunity for dependable use with the right attention. A sensible choice for buyers who recognize value and want an honest, economical purchase.",
