    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly car with plenty of life left in it? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest vehicle that could make a great runaround, first car, or little project for the right buyer. It\u2019s priced to reflect its age and condition, and for someone practical who doesn\u2019t mind a few rough edges, there\u2019s real value here. If you want something inexpensive and straightforward, come have a look.",
