      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Reliable budget-friendly project with solid bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts, runs, and drives, with a durable powertrain and straightforward mechanical layout that makes servicing and future upgrades easy. Cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections are present, but it\u2019s an honest driver with good parts value and strong potential for someone wanting affordable transportation or a hands-on build. Priced to move and well worth a look for the practical buyer.",
