      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a true underdog with plenty of story left to write. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who sees possibility where others see patina: a practical runabout, a hands-on project, or a budget-friendly set of wheels with personality to spare. If you appreciate machines with grit, soul, and the chance to make something your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
